query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(k mk) NoMergeJoin(k mk cc) NoNestLoop(cc k mk cct2) NoNestLoop(cc cct2 k mk cct1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 k mk mi_idx) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 k mi_idx mk it2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k mi_idx mk t) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k mi_idx mk t mi) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k mi mi_idx mk t it1) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it1 it2 k mi mi_idx mk t ci) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it1 it2 k mi mi_idx mk t n) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(n.name) AS writer,
min(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('10,000-mile-club',
'tv-special',
'based-on-comic',
'murder',
'based-on-novel',
'murder-in-title',
'homoeroticism')
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Action',
'Family',
'Drama',
'Horror',
'Sci-Fi',
'Horror')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(written by)')
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm';
